                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <desc>The name of the owner in the title has been carefully erased. It seems to have been <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሠርፀ፡ ድንግል፡</foreign>,
                                        possibly to be identified with <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8550sardaDe">Śarḍa Dǝngǝl</persName>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a1" corresp="#h2">
                                    <locus target="#152v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3509Epistle">1 John 1:1-7</title></desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2" corresp="#h3">
                                    <locus target="#1v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3509Epistle">1 John 1:1-7</title></desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3" corresp="#h4">
                                    <locus target="#153r"/>
                                    <desc type="MagicText">The following is the beginning:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ዓይን።</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a4" corresp="#h5">
                                    <locus target="#153r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5867Prayer">Śǝllus qǝddus mazgaba samāy</title></desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ መዝገበ፡ ሰማይ፡ ዓበይት፡ ዘትሁቡ፡ ዓስበ፡ በሰርከ፡ ዕለት፡ ለቀደምት፡ ወለደኃርት፡</q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a5">
                                    <locus from="4r" to="27v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">On the vacant portion of each leaf, the <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir</title> is written:
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Trinity">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir: Mystery of the Trinity ()</title> begins on <locus target="#12v"/>;
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Incarnation">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir: Mystery of the Incarnation ()</title> begins on <locus target="#15v"/>;
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#BaptismMystery">No item: LIT1097Ammest, could not check for BaptismMystery</title> begins on <locus target="#20r"/>;
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Eucharist">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir: Mystery of the Eucharist ()</title> begins on <locus target="#23r"/>;
                                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1097Ammest#Resurrection">ʾAmmǝstu ʾaʿmāda mǝśṭir: Mystery of the Resurrection ()</title> begins on <locus target="#25v"/>.
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="am"/>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e2">
                                    <locus from="2r"/>
                                    <desc>Musical notes have occasionally been added by a later hand to <ref target="#ms_i1.1"/>.</desc>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="e3">
                                    <locus from="2r"/>
                                    <desc>Various titles have been added to the Psalms by a later hand in <ref target="#ms_i1.1"/>, 
                                        usually in the upper margins. Apparently the textblock was trimmed before binding, through which these titles were

                                    mostly destroyed.</desc>

                                </item>
                                
                            </list>
                        </additions>
